---
// src/pages/ultimate-creator-laptops.astro
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
const affiliateCreatorWorkstation = "https://www.amazon.com/s?k=16-inch+workstation+laptop&tag=laptopvette-20";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="The Ultimate Creator Laptops of 2026 - LaptopVette"
    description="A deep-dive review of the best creator laptops of 2026, covering performance, display, and workflow suitability."
    path="/ultimate-creator-laptops"
    type="article"
  />
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container"><a href="/" class="logo">Laptop<span>Vette</span></a></div>
  </nav>

  <article class="article-container">
    <header class="article-header">
      <span class="category-tag">Buying Guides</span>
      <h1>The Ultimate Creator Laptops of 2026: Deep Dive Review</h1>
      <p class="byline">Published July 2026 • 12 Min Read</p>
    </header>

    <div class="disclosure-box">
      <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> LaptopVette is an independent site. When you purchase through links on this page, we may earn an affiliate commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="review-block">
      <h2>1. Premium Workstation 16" (Best Overall)</h2>
      <p>The clear winner for intensive video editing and 3D modeling pipelines this year. During heavy rendering loops, its thermal configuration kept noise down while maintaining high boost clocks.</p>
      
      <div class="specs-table">
        <h4>Technical Specifications</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Processor:</strong> M5 Max (16-Core CPU, 40-Core GPU)</li>
          <li><strong>Memory:</strong> 64GB Unified Architecture</li>
          <li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2TB PCIe NVMe SSD</li>
          <li><strong>Display:</strong> 16.2-inch Liquid Retina XDR (120Hz Mini-LED)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="action-box">
        <div>
          <h3>Ready to buy the Premium Workstation 16"?</h3>
          <p>Check current pricing and customer reviews through the retailer links provided.</p>
        </div>
        <a href={affiliateCreatorWorkstation} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored nofollow" aria-label="Check pricing on Amazon (affiliate)" class="btn btn-buy">Check current pricing →</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

</body>
</html>

<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.85; }
  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .navbar { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 0; }
  .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: #0f172a; }
  .logo span { color: #b91c1c; }
  
  .article-container { max-width: 1064px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 40px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .category-tag { color: #b91c1c; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px; }
  h1 { font-size: 36px; margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.2; }
  .byline { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
  
  .disclosure-box { background: #f1f5f9; border-left: 4px solid #64748b; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; font-size: 14px; }
  h2 { margin: 56px 0 22px 0; font-size: 22px; color: #1e1b4b; font-weight: 700; border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c; padding-left: 15px; }
  .review-block p { margin-bottom: 1.4em; line-height: 1.85; text-align: justify; color: #334155; }
  .specs-table h4 { margin-bottom: 10px; color: #0f172a; }
  .specs-table ul { list-style: none; }
  .specs-table li { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 15px; }

  .action-box { background: #fff1f2; border: 2px dashed #b91c1c; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .action-box { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; } }
  .action-box h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .action-box p { font-size: 14px; color: #475569; }
  
  .btn-buy { display: inline-block; background: #f59e0b; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 6px; white-space: nowrap; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .btn-buy:hover { background: #d97706; }
</style>